    "16560502492171dd33": {
      "type": "loop-article-richtext",
      "blocks": {
        "16560502493ef96db8-0": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>They even help with relieving irritating ear pain by equalizing the pressure against your ear drum. And when you drift off to sleep, they’re super safe and comfortable to keep wearing.<\/p><p>Earplugs like <a href=\"https:\/\/www.loopearplugs.com\/products\/quiet\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Loop Quiet<\/span><\/a> are not only reusable but can also reduce noise levels by 27 decibels, making them ideal for sleeping while traveling. For more on earplugs to help you sleep, check out our <a href=\"https:\/\/www.loopearplugs.com\/blogs\/blog\/earplugs-for-sleeping\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">blog post<\/span><\/a> here. <\/p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "16560502493ef96db8-0"
