    "00e89fc7-bcb7-4e16-a890-cedfb227e0d6": {
      "type": "loop-article-img-txt",
      "blocks": {
        "template--15759384150212__00e89fc7-bcb7-4e16-a890-cedfb227e0d6-166696322120e94c4c-0": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "4) Leave your stress at home",
            "heading_size": "h2"
          }
        },
        "template--15759384150212__00e89fc7-bcb7-4e16-a890-cedfb227e0d6-166696322120e94c4c-1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Planning trips can be stressful. Have I packed all I need? What if I can’t sleep on vacation? Bet I’ll forget my passport!!! <\/p><p>Stop, take a breather, and leave your stress at the door. <\/p><p>Why not try mindfulness meditation? Mindful breathing can have a huge effect on reducing insomnia and encourage an overall better sleep. <\/p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "template--15759384150212__00e89fc7-bcb7-4e16-a890-cedfb227e0d6-166696322120e94c4c-0",
